---
import SidebarLayout from '../../../layouts/SidebarLayout.astro';
import "../../../styles/global.css";
---

<SidebarLayout app="css">
  <h1 class="text-xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-5 text-custom-accent text-center">
    CSS Typography
  </h1>

  <section class="mb-5 space-y-6 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed text-custom-secondary">
    <p>
      Typography is crucial for readability and user experience. CSS provides extensive control over fonts, text styling, and text layout.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-custom-accent mt-6 mb-3">Font Properties</h2>

    <div class="bg-custom-secondary border border-custom rounded-lg p-3 sm:p-4 my-4">
      <pre class="text-xs sm:text-sm overflow-x-auto whitespace-pre-wrap"><code>{`body {
  /* Font family with fallbacks */
  font-family: 'Inter', 'Arial', sans-serif;
  
  /* Font size and weight */
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 400;
  
  /* Line height for readability */
  line-height: 1.6;
  
  /* Text transformation */
  text-transform: none;
  font-style: normal;
}

.heading {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.2;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
}`}</code></pre>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-custom-accent mt-6 mb-3">Text Styling</h2>

    <div class="bg-custom-secondary border border-custom rounded-lg p-3 sm:p-4 my-4">
      <pre class="text-xs sm:text-sm overflow-x-auto whitespace-pre-wrap"><code>{`.text-element {
  /* Text color and alignment */
  color: #333;
  text-align: left;
  
  /* Text decoration */
  text-decoration: none;
  text-decoration: underline;
  
  /* Text spacing */
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  word-spacing: 2px;
  
  /* Text effects */
  text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  text-transform: uppercase;
}`}</code></pre>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-custom-secondary border border-custom rounded-2xl p-4 sm:p-6 mt-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-custom-accent mb-3">Web Fonts</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 pl-4">
        <li>Use <code class="bg-custom-primary text-custom-secondary px-1 rounded text-sm">@font-face</code> for custom fonts</li>
        <li>Google Fonts provides easy-to-use web fonts</li>
        <li>Consider font loading performance with <code class="bg-custom-primary text-custom-secondary px-1 rounded text-sm">font-display: swap</code></li>
        <li>Provide fallback fonts for better compatibility</li>
        <li>Use relative units (em, rem) for responsive typography</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</SidebarLayout>